text:
Thank you for today.
Thanks to both of you, it was really fun♪

Being told I resemble the heroine of a musical... 
That made me really happy too!

Since that heroine was my role model...
It meant a lot to me.

Hehe, in that case, maybe someday
a girl will look up to Chiyuki-san too!

Is that so...
Hehe, it would be nice if that happened.

Chiyuki-san...
Let's go out together again sometime, okay?
(...Today had a lot of different things going on.)

(Being someone's role model...
I never imagined that, but--)
